<p>
<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svasti śrīmannaḷagiripatērddē</hi>
<lb n="2" break="no"/><hi rend="grantha">vadēvasya dēvyāḥ pitrājasrā vi</hi>
<lb n="3" break="no"/><hi rend="grantha">rahamacalādhīśvarēṇaiva ka</hi>
<lb n="4"/><hi rend="grantha"><supplied reason="omitted">r</supplied>ttum <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:ddanda" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> Ētattādṛnni</hi><note n="165-1">Two letters have been omitted here.</note> <hi rend="grantha">Ivōtbhāsa</hi>
<lb n="5" break="no"/><hi rend="grantha">mānam vimānam vīraścakrē mala</hi>
<lb n="6" break="no"/><hi rend="grantha">yajamahīmaṇḍana<unclear>m</unclear> sundarēśaḥ</hi><note n="165-2">Metre: Mandākrantā.</note> <hi rend="grantha"><g type="pc"/></hi>
</p>

